PROCESSES:
- ps - list of running processes
- ps aux - list of all processes (also system)
- top - actual processes
- kill <PID> - terminates the process
- sigterm - kill the process, but allow to do a cleanup
- sigkill - kill the process, don't do cleanup
- sigstop - stop the process


